Home of Scality Droplet, a cloud storage client library.
Scality - http://www.scality.com

Scality Droplet is open source and released under the BSD License.

Mission: Help the transition to object based cloud storage by providing a
structured API to simplify application developers job and address key user
concerns.

All source code is hosted here, documentation is also available here in the
wiki section: http://github.com/scality/Droplet/wiki

The doxygen generated documentation is also available here: http://scality.github.io/Droplet

Please report bugs, comments and questions to
http://groups.google.com/group/scality-scop. You can also reach us on 
the #droplet IRC channel on Freenode.
